Title: Object: Maria fugiens in Egiptum
Series: Vita et historia beatae Mariae virginis matris Dei
Description: Flight into Egypt, with Virgin and Child riding a donkey and St Joseph walking by their side, going to left; proof before letter. c.1633/34 Etching
Curator's comments: From a set of fourteen, see 1861,0713.135 for comment.
Bibliographic references: Meaume 1860 / Recherches sur la vie et les ouvrages de Jacques Callot (85) (undescribed state, before letter)
Acquisition notes: From the Scarisbrick collection of Callot's work: see comment on 1861,0713.1.
